# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 📧 EMAIL CONFIGURATION - REQUIRED FOR INVOICE DELIVERY
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 🎯 PURPOSE: Send professional invoice emails to customers automatically
#
# 📋 SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
#
# 1. Get Gmail App Password:
#    → Visit: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    → Enable 2-Step Verification if not already enabled
#    → Generate App Password for "Mail" app
#    → Copy the 16-character password (remove spaces)
#
# 2. Update the values below:
#    → Replace "your-email@gmail.com" with your actual Gmail
#    → Replace "your-16-character-app-password" with the app password
#    → DO NOT use quotes around the values
#    → DO NOT include spaces in the app password
#
# 3. Restart the server:
#    → Stop: Ctrl+C
#    → Start: npm run dev
#
# 4. Test it:
#    → Place an order
#    → Check console for success message
#    → Check customer email inbox
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY:
#    → Never commit this file to Git (already in .gitignore)
#    → Never share your App Password
#    → Use App Password, NOT your regular Gmail password
#
# 📚 MORE HELP: See EMAIL_SETUP_GUIDE.md and QUICK_EMAIL_SETUP.txt
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Replace with your actual Gmail address
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com

# Replace with your 16-character Gmail App Password (no spaces)
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-16-character-app-password

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ✅ EXAMPLE (after setup):
# EMAIL_USER=organicstore@gmail.com
# EMAIL_PASSWORD=abcdefghijklmnop
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

